  "title": "Xtra Quick Irish Beef Flank Steak Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and quick-fix Irish dish featuring beef flank steak in a mustardy and glassy-jelly broth, perfect for a weeknight dinner. This stew is also anti-inflammatory-friendly.",
